<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3900356>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cellaria calculosa n. sp., TAN307/79. A. Internode with autozooids and avicularia. B. Opesia with condyles. C. Interzooidal avicularium. D. Distal tip of internode with rootlet pores and avicularium. E. Proximal end of internode with paired avicularia and autozooids with well-developed rootlet pores. Scale bars: A, D, 500 μm; B, C, 100 μm; E, 300 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3900356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

